    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "薄暗い森を抜け、ついに目的地である廃病院に\n無事、到着しました。これから内部を……きゃっ！？",
      "startTime": 4.6688647214,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_light-down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7500.000000000001,
          "startTime": 8.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "つ、机が勝手に動いてる！？　これは千紗の大好きな\n生のポルターガイスト現象、生ポルというものでは！？",
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9778.187489499998,
          "startTime": 25.0448541562
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　これはこの廃病院に巣食う悪霊のせい？\nこのメモに従って悪霊を退治しなくちゃいけない！？",
      "startTime": 24.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5147.8460867999975,
          "startTime": 29.9145127535
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（急に除霊を強いるなんて、かなり強引な流れで）\n（繋いできたな。さすがにバレるんじゃないか……！？）",
      "startTime": 31.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（いやむしろ、姉の威厳を保つためには気付いた方が）\n（いいはず！　頼む、そろそろ気付いてくれ！）",
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました！　まずはここに書かれている呪文を\n三回詠唱する……っ、いきます！",
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "とすぺんてのきつ、とすぺんてのきつ……\n声を大きく？　っ、はい！　とすぺんてのきつ！",
      "startTime": 54.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6672.902162899994,
          "startTime": 60.8729021629
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（それは月のテンペストを逆さまにしているだけだぞ！）\n（くうっ、これ以上は沙季の知的なイメージが心配だ！）",
      "startTime": 63.2723645288,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6894.302137899998,
          "startTime": 70.1666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7627.635471200008,
          "startTime": 70.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "そして次は、お辞儀を二回！　拍手を二回！\nそして最後にお辞儀を一回！",
      "startTime": 71.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "っ！？　これ、初詣の作法と同じ手順のような\nえっ！？　まさか、これって――",
      "startTime": 79.8368633855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（おぉ！　ついに気付いてくれたか、沙季！）",
      "startTime": 82.848117002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "悪霊伝説と初詣が何か関係しているのかもしれません！\n効果があるなら、何度もやりましょう！　悪霊退散！",
      "startTime": 91.4491610043,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8667.503119300009,
          "startTime": 100.1166641236
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10217.503119300005,
          "startTime": 101.6666641236
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（真面目過ぎる！　あと妙なところで天然過ぎるぞ沙季）\n（これは最後まで気付かないかもしれないな）",
      "startTime": 99.5701799524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "二礼二拍手一礼を終えたら、大幣を――\nえ？　大幣が用意出来てない！？",
      "startTime": 109.0921092444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうすれば……え？　かわりにサイリウムですか？\nこのサイリウムにはアイドルなら『気』を込められる？",
      "startTime": 118.3666671754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "祝詞を読みながら、これを振ればいいんですね\nわ、分かりませんけど分かりました、やります！",
      "startTime": 125.7666671754,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5524.294980499988,
          "startTime": 131.2909621559
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（『気』がどうとかいうレベルじゃないだろう）\n（なぜ悪霊を祓うのにサイリウムを使うんだ！）",
      "startTime": 132.7794414364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "読む祝詞は……え？　本当にこれでいいんですか？\nこんなことがあるとは不思議ですが……",
      "startTime": 141.6333338421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "今度、私が出演する映画が公開されます\n悪霊さんも、ぜひ観て下さいねっ！",
      "startTime": 148.6133046522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（もう祝詞でもなんでもなくなっている！）\n（ただ映画の宣伝を差し込みたかっただけじゃないか）",
      "startTime": 154.6666671754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（っと、そろそろロケのオチの時間だな）\n（この後、悪霊に扮した千紗が出てくるはずだが……）",
      "startTime": 161.9000005087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あ、あの、廊下の奥……誰かいませんか！？\n真っ赤に染まった服を着た、あれは……千紗？",
      "startTime": 171.9333338421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（え？　一瞬で千紗だと気付いた？）\n（プロが施した特殊メイクだぞ……！？）",
      "startTime": 182.1333338421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ですよね？　だって立ち方が千紗ですし\nどうしてあんな格好……",
      "startTime": 188.2333338421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon"
